property.value:
This model requires contains a FMU generated from a JModelica .mo file.
The .fmu file has binaries for darwin64 and linux64.
Note that under Linux the .fmu file has fairly tight dependencies on the version of Fortran and GLibC.
Under Mac OS X, the .fmu file depends on Lapack and Blas. It might be necessary to install JModelica, see https://svn.jmodelica.org/trunk/INSTALL and http://chess.eecs.berkeley.edu/ptexternal/wiki/Main/JModelica
The suppressWarnings flag is set because otherwise we get an error when we set hc.hx.
The output is strange because t7 does not match the value from the plot, but cabin_t does?
